### Heuristic Ideas:

- Assign the item to the bin with the least space (smallest remaining bin).
- Assign the item to the bin with the most space (largest remaining bin).
- Assign the item to the bin with the smallest bin that can fit the item.
- Assign the item to the bin with the largest bin that can fit the item.
- Assign the priority based on some combination of these factors.

